{"tid":816400,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你 醒未","createTime":"2018-09-12T17:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T14:01:04.000Z","uid":59569,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"df794ffd2d93e04bc1226eb65ecdc34038626a80","tid":816400,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:12:08.000Z","msg":"佢走左啦 唔會再返黎啦<br />\n佢已經唔會再介入你既生活，你地係條平行線啊，冇相連既時候。<br />\n講真，你痛苦定開心，佢都唔會知亦都唔想知啊。<br />\n就算你放棄你的人生，放棄成個森林。佢都唔會揀你做佢棵樹。<br />\n<br />\n我係你就裝備現在，迎接將來。<br />\n雖然我對愛情都冇咩信心，但我都唔敢講將來會冇希望。<br />\n因為我知道我唔努力，將來就一定俾唔到幸福人同追求幸福。"},{"pid":"2f3e63c557761e7b4c9a9245b093595b952efb2f","tid":816400,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"努力還是會傷心"},{"pid":"e9acff0260d2efc5139105e4fa5571b4b374bb92","tid":816400,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"佢想你自動自覺收嗲啊， 點解你條懵撚仲要開post問 ?"},{"pid":"23ff8261938487941bcd7b37cdd11725766e2fee","tid":816400,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"bc0454b87781851ffbbf3caa99ee208b8317fb36","tid":816400,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"係交叉線"},{"pid":"f8c432a3e61fa2534a0f44f078c0405391500856","tid":816400,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9acff0260d2efc5139105e4fa5571b4b374bb92","tid":816400,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"佢想你自動自覺收嗲啊， 點解你條懵撚仲要開post問 ?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"問乜柒<br />\n死中女俾仔飛到中文字都唔識睇?"},{"pid":"3e35e2edfc673b09a05ddeaa205c5c33d8dc80f5","tid":816400,"uid":167637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8c432a3e61fa2534a0f44f078c0405391500856","tid":816400,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"